des:
Meditate me helps the user to meditate in almost all settings and not taking much of his time. It focuses on laying out the stress and boost the productivity of the meditator, giving him the ability to believe in himself.

>> Meditation which is affective and time-boxed, because who really has time.
>> Gather all your energy and channel it to a particular task.
>> Increases productivity and mindfulness.
>> No nature irrelevant nature sounds to let you actually be with you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
